{"tid":745761,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【中年失業】53歲原練馬師 見完馬會宣佈玩完","createTime":"2018-07-17T05:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T07:35:44.000Z","uid":50740,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"687ae799eaf77bd2a3c8403c0f19c572e34160ce","tid":745761,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"馬會今午（16日）公佈，牌照委員會於今天的會議上，聆聽了李易達就為何他提出的2018/2019年度馬季練馬師牌照申請，應獲批准所陳述的理由。<br />\n<br />\n委員會裁定李易達的申請不成功，因此李易達就上述馬季提出的練馬師牌照申請已被拒絕。<br />\n李易達即時不再是香港練馬師，未來動向亦未明。<br />\n在這情況下，現年53歲的李易達將不能連續第15季在港從練，而他於過去14個從練季度內，共勝出349場賽事。<br />\n李易達在2012/13及2013/14年度馬季，分別只勝出11場及12場頭馬，連續兩季成績不達標。<br />\n今季他一直陷於苦戰，煞科日（15日）連場出擊，可惜未能取得救命一Win，最終只以15Win完季，差一Win才上岸，變成累積三季不達標，不符合再獲續牌的要求，因而踏上網民所說的中年失業之路。<br />\n在李易達及告達理馬房解散後，來季將有22位練馬師在港設廐，當中包括最新獲發牌的丁冠豪。<br />\n告達理全季埋單僅獲13場頭馬，亦達不到續牌指標。他早於煞科前已向馬會表明，一旦成績不達標，便不會爭取來季牌照。<br />\n在這大前提下，告達理不需像李易達那樣，面見牌委會作最後爭取<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3ad5634e4b675272a235abd5b26965ce360fa2","tid":745761,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"之後都無？"},{"pid":"f240ec66cd6cad6d595f85ac43a9d2e12036e2f4","tid":745761,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"其實馬會個制度都幾pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2f8894c91b496a717f8a3f5efaec07af1e5133","tid":745761,"uid":118710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f240ec66cd6cad6d595f85ac43a9d2e12036e2f4","tid":745761,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"其實馬會個制度都幾pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:23:30.000Z","msg":"三次機會啦"},{"pid":"29bcb6e39dfb61e8f833f76aa4b08e757af4268b","tid":745761,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8730cd832e59b9f03dd38675db7600c53fad53fc","tid":745761,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"全季千幾場馬咁都無15w,抵啦"},{"pid":"a0332c1c2fd8a87fec690f893268f645b3a0339d","tid":745761,"uid":137627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"大告一直以來兵源唔多就無得講，衰仔達以前都好多支持<br />\n自己古撚惑惑不學無術，咁鍾意燉咪燉埋個牌囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b643c2b6fe6785075a61829549f84f341f4b1f2","tid":745761,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"練馬師比人炒左可以做咩？<br />\n<br />\n馬夫得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e85a10148f99007e388567843bb17edcce488b","tid":745761,"uid":10843,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:03:04.000Z","msg":"十幾年搵既錢都夠退休啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔退休都可以去第二到教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe69df6417f73c7f7e3de39f8d5da2e1632ec565","tid":745761,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:07:36.000Z","msg":"多謝楊明綸啦，師傅馬都跑到成pat屎咁，正垃圾"},{"pid":"6178cac96de54eb8bb975a18c13727278535b72f","tid":745761,"uid":154661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"告東尼同鄭俊偉好波，整死呢個奸仔達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f602641f37137228e39d7611daf3717b38d96fde","tid":745761,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e85a10148f99007e388567843bb17edcce488b","tid":745761,"uid":10843,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:03:04.000Z","msg":"十幾年搵既錢都夠退休啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔退休都可以去第二到教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa